OL,6,FWet wipes that are flushed down the
OL,7,Ftoilet instead of being thrown in the
OL,8,Fbin are contributing to fatbergs
OL,9,Fclogging the water network, according
OL,10,Fto South West Water (SWW).
OL,12,FThe water company estimates 12 tonnes
OL,13,Fof solid waste is filtered out of
OL,14,Fdrainage works at its Countess Wear
OL,15,Fsite on the edge of Exeter every month.
