OL,3,CTonnes of waste flushed into Devon and
OL,4,CCornwall water network
OL,6,FIt comes as the "Fine to Flush"
OL,7,Fbranding on hygiene wipes is being
OL,8,Fdropped, with the water industry
OL,9,Fadmitting customers are confused about
OL,10,Fwhat should or should not go down the
OL,11,Floo.
OL,13,FIt's hoped new guidance on wet wipes
OL,14,Fwill help bring an end to clogged-up
OL,15,Fsewers and fatbergs - a mass of waste
OL,16,Fmatter in sewers formed by non-
OL,17,Fbiodegradable solids - in waterways.
