OL,3,CTonnes of waste flushed into Devon and
OL,4,CCornwall water network
OL,6,FHelen Dobby, the Head of Environmental
OL,7,FPerformance at South West Water, said:
OL,8,F"We empty four full skips of wet
OL,9,Fwipes, rags, and sanitary products in
OL,10,Fa week.
OL,12,F"That's 12 tonnes every month so the
OL,13,Fequivalent of a double decker bus
OL,14,Fgoing out of the site every month."
OL,16,FCurrently nearly 3 billion wet wipes
OL,17,Fend up in Britain's waterways each
OL,18,Fyear and it's hoped the new rules will
OL,19,Fprevent fatbergs .
