OL,6,FWhile many companies have responded to
OL,7,Fcustomer demands to be more
OL,8,Fenvironmentally friendly by claiming
OL,9,Fto be plastic free or 100%
OL,10,Fbiodegradable, it doesn't mean they
OL,11,Fare flushable.
OL,13,FMost do carry a 'don't flush' warning
OL,14,Fand a spokesperson from Water UK said:
OL,15,F"Thanks to Fine to Flush, the majority
OL,16,Fof hygiene wipes have changed their
OL,17,Fdesign to a less environmentally
OL,18,Fharmful formulation.
