OL,4,CCornwall water network
OL,6,F"Following recent advice from the
OL,7,FGovernment we are now focused on
OL,8,Furging customers to dispose of wet
OL,9,Fwipes appropriately through the Bin
OL,10,Fthe Wipe campaign."
OL,12,FSome products are even sold as
OL,13,Fflushable, but South West Water says
OL,14,Fthey can still cause blockages.
OL,16,FHelen said: "The message we'd like
OL,17,Fpeople to remember is that wet wipes
OL,18,Fdo block pipes.
