OL,6,F"Even when a product is marketed as
OL,7,Fbeing flushable, we would absolutely
OL,8,Fsay to folk 'use the bin in the
OL,9,Fbathroom'.
OL,11,F"Use an alternative to wet wipes in
OL,12,Fthe first place and just think about
OL,13,Fwhat goes down the loo".
OL,15,FTypically South West Water has to deal
OL,16,Fwith more than 7,000 blockages right
OL,17,Facross the network and that equates to
OL,18,Fa cost of #4.4 million.
